Originated from https://github.com/thesues/robot_sft @ 07c131b93e704f65a5bb7106fc58bc76aa101b56
(an Isaac GR00T SFT orchestrator).

Ported in-place to target HuggingFace lerobot's `lerobot-train` end to end: launch/resume
commands, checkpoint anatomy (checkpoints/<step>/{pretrained_model,training_state} + last),
held-out episode split via --dataset.episodes (no dataset copy), and open-loop offline eval
(scripts/offline_eval.py) instead of GR00T's open_loop_eval.py. Maintained here directly —
this is no longer a verbatim mirror of the upstream repo.
